Category:Unidentified Jedi of the New Jedi Order

nodes.text: This unidentified reptilian Jedi trainee was a female Jedi student at Luke Skywalker's Jedi Praxeum on Yavin 4 in 12 ABY. She was present at a meeting inside the Great Temple that was held just after the Galactic Empire began an attack on the academy, to decide what the Jedi could do. As Dorsk 81 began talking about how the Jedi could increase their powers by working together, she asked him what they could actually do against the Imperial threat and he explained to her that the Jedi could use the Massassi temples to focus their combined powers and move the attacking Star Destroyers away.
